HEADWORD: Cycloscope
<hw>Cy"clo*scope</hw> <pr>(s?"kl?-sk?p)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Cyclo-</ets> + <ets>-scope</ets>.]</ety> <def>A machine for
measuring at any moment velocity of rotation, as of a wheel of a steam
engine.</def> <rj><au>Knight.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

